name: Dinari QQQ
description: The Dinari QQQ dShares token (QQQ.d) represents 1:1 ownership of shares in the Invesco QQQ ETF, a fund that tracks the performance of the Nasdaq-100 Index, which includes the largest non-financial companies in the Nasdaq stock market. Each QQQ.d token is fully backed by a corresponding share of the ETF securely held in a transparent and auditable treasury. By leveraging blockchain technology, QQQ.d provides investors with seamless access to the Nasdaq-100, enabling 24/7 trading, fractional ownership, instant settlement, and enhanced liquidity.
